rows.label: qst701402_msg0002
rows.name:
Tizza Parisax are swarming
all over Braying Canyon.

rows.label: qst701402_msg0003
rows.name:
If we don't do something
about them, we can't transport
this food to Aletta.

rows.label: qst701402_msg0004
rows.name:
Everyone, I'm sorry to trouble
you again, but please help us.

rows.label: qst701402_msg0102
rows.name:
You've driven away the Tizza
Parisax, haven't you?

rows.label: qst701402_msg0104
rows.name:
Eh? If we have this Pestronella
Oil, we won't be attacked?

rows.label: qst701402_msg0106
rows.name:
As expected of Adel-sama
and the others!

rows.label: qst701402_msg0107
rows.name:
Because the Tizza Parisax would
go extinct, you chose a peaceful
method without defeating them.

rows.label: qst701402_msg0108
rows.name:
To consider not only the
people of Iira, but also
the monsters of Iira...

rows.label: qst701402_msg0109
rows.name:
Could it be that if the
ecosystem is destroyed, it
could lead to food problems?

rows.label: qst701402_msg0110
rows.name: Wow... I am filled with admiration.

rows.label: qst701402_msg0111
rows.name:
I, Ivan, will serve Adel-sama
with my whole body and soul
until I can repay this debt!

rows.label: qst701402_msg0112
rows.name:
Oh, this isn't the time to be impressed.
If I don't get this food back quickly,
Augusto-san and everyone will yell at me.

rows.label: qst701402_msg0113
rows.name:
Well then, we'll be on our way...
Please visit Aletta again.
